<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Approval needed</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #222; line-height: 1.5;">
  <h2 style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Hello {{approverName}},</h2>

  <p style="margin-top: 0;">
    A new monitor registration is awaiting your approval.
  </p>

  <div style="border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-radius:10px;padding:12px 14px;background:#f9fafb;">
    <p style="margin:0 0 8px;"><strong>Name:</strong> {{registrantName}}</p>
    <p style="margin:0 0 8px;"><strong>Email:</strong> {{registrantEmail}}</p>
    <p style="margin:0;"><strong>Town:</strong> {{town}}</p>
  </div>

  <p style="margin: 16px 0;">
    <a href="{{approvalsUrl}}" style="background:#2563eb;color:#fff;padding:10px 16px;text-decoration:none;border-radius:6px;">
      Open approvals
    </a>
  </p>

  <p>If the button does not work, copy and paste this URL into your browser:</p>
  <p style="word-break: break-all;">{{approvalsUrl}}</p>

  <p style="margin-top:24px;">Thank you,<br/>LRC Jeunesse</p>
</body>
</html>

